      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Originally contained a Greek dedication that was later replaced with an Aramaic one. Repair is evident, as the white tesserae serving as the background for the Aramaic inscription are slightly different from those in the original mosaic. The date of repair is unknown.</p>
         </div>
